{"tid":1751013,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"小弟有幾樣嘢想提大家","createTime":"2019-11-24T15:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T17:24:18.000Z","uid":229502,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d7d7c5914e27934ca7365c1b2140432e10283eb9","tid":1751013,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:15:53.000Z","msg":"小弟平時寫開戰爭故，對戰爭頗有認識，無奈幾日前先搵返acc，依家先可以提各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.停止內部分化同埋整頓士氣<br />\n2.增加宣傳<br />\n3.令國際知道發生乜事，有外國frd就全部講晒<br />\n4.保持樂觀主義<br />\n5.唔好令負面事件影響自己，要化悲憤為動力<br />\n6.強身健體<br />\n7.行動時唔好落單<br />\n8.行動時着黑風褸，加快換裝速度<br />\n9.見到「便衣狗」時，唔好幾個人一齊衝埋去，最好唔好打到傷晒，骨折等，「打死唔知好唔好呢? (梗係唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)」<br />\n10.遇到分化嘅人，請無視，唔好引述或回應<br />\n11.罷光顧藍商鋪 (不止食店)<br />\n12.同身邊嘅人齊上齊落，互相鼓勵<br />\n13.要走一齊走，或如有人數優勢 (&gt;5-10&lt;倍) ，一齊對抗防暴<br />\n14.和理非都要買gear，預防突發事件<br />\n15.請尊重手足合理嘅決定<br />\n16.如有意見分歧，請以安全及可行性為先<br />\n17.行動時唔好夢遊，要隨時打醒十二分精神<br />\n18.如有行動資料請勿在大庭廣眾下發佈，因為會有mon po狗偷睇，可以喺信得過嘅人之間分發，但如果係吹雞，咁就冇所謂<br />\n19.唔好有人叫走就走，睇清楚情況先<br />\n20.如安全，請盡力救出被狗捉住嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n我諗到再提大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 : 本文內容為本人作品「你是一名在戰場上的無名士兵」之附錄，與現實完全無關，請各位切勿將本文內容與現實混為一談<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e533f99a005aa08fea41bf653ee1d627770c5f7","tid":1751013,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:17:15.000Z","msg":"teoi1"},{"pid":"a1d2f2655d5c0aba434fefb283096ae30c2e834f","tid":1751013,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:18:34.000Z","msg":"teoi2"},{"pid":"87cb3c67c8844367edfd169a3e2504a10fc31b9e","tid":1751013,"uid":249162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:22:32.000Z","msg":"所有行動時請check清楚衣物鞋帶有冇好好固定"},{"pid":"0b7084b915d31754cc470e8879b3720a5ca2dec9","tid":1751013,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87cb3c67c8844367edfd169a3e2504a10fc31b9e","tid":1751013,"uid":249162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:22:32.000Z","msg":"所有行動時請check清楚衣物鞋帶有冇好好固定"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c2535cb9187445c972fafac5d51c8b729c2571","tid":1751013,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"teoi3"},{"pid":"2b2da254200d9ee8b93dc3a945539d54ad19b1f0","tid":1751013,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:36:37.000Z","msg":"teoi4"},{"pid":"a37c6a79a77121722a53e4a24cae1727ca94fd39","tid":1751013,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:49:20.000Z","msg":"teoi5"},{"pid":"479de978c14f67c497f1067f2320aa56b3335365","tid":1751013,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:05:13.000Z","msg":"teoi6"},{"pid":"532afef75babaa9da88872d16e147c6977f42fdc","tid":1751013,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:24:18.000Z","msg":"teoi7"}]}